<div class="help-content-wrap"><h3 id="how-to-play-sports">How to Play &quot;Sports&quot;</h3>
<ol>
<li>Tap the &quot;Sports&quot; tab. Filter events by time, sports and/or league.</li>
<li>View the &quot;popular&quot; events area in the Home page for recommended events such as &quot;Today&#39;s Football&quot;, &quot;English Premier League&quot; and many other recommended events.</li>
<li>View important prematch games in the &quot;Highlights&quot; area.</li>
<li>Browse ongoing live betting games or virtuals to place a bet.</li>
<li>We do not only provide sports betting for Football, but we also provide all kinds of bets for other sports.</li>
<li>Choose events you wish to play and select the odds by clicking on them. The chosen selections (no more than 30) will be automatically added to the betslip.</li>
<li>The value of every single stake should always be between Ksh50-500,000. Click on &quot;Place Bet&quot; and &quot;Confirm&quot; the bet to place it.</li>
<li>A message will be displayed to inform whether a bet has been successfully placed or not.</li>
</ol>
